%^CYAN%^BOLD%^GLADIATOR%^RESET%^

Your tactic is not to simply attack, but to maneuver your enemies into the most optimal position, forcibly if necessary.

%^BOLD%^Trance:%^RESET%^
Skill Bonus : Influence
Trance Bonus : Combat Maneuver and Combat Maneuver Defense Bonus

